BusinessTech will hold its Online FinTech Conference on 20 July 2022, and it is set to be a great event. The BusinessTech Online FinTech Conference is an event for banking, ICT, and FinTech executives and professionals. The conference will cover a variety of topics, including FinTech disruption, mobile payments, digital banking, cryptocurrency, blockchain, and more. Over 2,000 delegates are set to attend the online event, which will be hosted on a dedicated event platform. BusinessTech has secured great speakers for the online conference. The Online FinTech Conference will be hosted by respected business personality Michael Avery. Avery will then interview the country’s top FinTech players. This includes: Nedbank Divisional Executive of Emerging Payments – Chipo Mushwana
